      "updated": 1700000000000, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "③ Parse XHTML → Plain Text\nBeautifulSoup (lxml-xml parser)\nConverts Confluence storage format\nto readable plain text\n───────────────────\nHeadings, lists, tables → markdown\nMacros included as text",
