      "updated": 1700000000000, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "④ Lyzr Agent API\nCalled once per page\nProduces page-level intelligence\n───────────────────\nPOST /v3/inference/chat/\n→ summary  (2-4 sentences)\n→ tags  (3-8 topic tags)\n→ relevancy_score  (0.0–1.0)",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "baseline": 11,
      "containerId": "s7",
      "originalText": "④ Lyzr Agent API\nCalled once per page\nProduces page-level intelligence\n───────────────────\nPOST /v3/inference/chat/\n→ summary  (2-4 sentences)\n→ tags  (3-8 topic tags)\n→ relevancy_score  (0.0–1.0)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
